author: Brian Heater
title: Sennheiser’s Momentum True Wireless 2 are a great-sounding pair of $300 earbuds
description: They’re doing construction in my apartment building right now. I live on the first floor and can hear the distinct sound of jackhammering on concrete coming from the basement below. There’s also the sound of a generator and a far higher-pitched drilling noise…
